        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_pro/scenes/missions/miami/scene_flamingo.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository 02ec00db-dc54-4ce6-8d87-3657ff59440a).Image",
        "Description": "Kronstradt has begun to monopolize the market and is avoiding antitrust laws by making shell companies that act as distribution centers in the US and Canada. Our client, a disgruntled ex-CEO who sold his company to robert Knox only for it to be broken down into distribution centers, wants the Knox family dynasty to be put to rest by executing Robert and his highest level engineers and designers, plummeting their stock price and leaving the company in the hands of Knox&apos;s impulsive daughter.",
